---
import Header from '../components/Header';
import Hero from '../components/Hero';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar';
import NewsletterModal from '../components/NewsletterModal';
import SkipLink from '../components/SkipLink';
import SEO from '../components/SEO';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Demo Page with Placeholder Content</title>
    <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json" />
    <SEO client:load title="Demo Page" description="A demo page with placeholder images and articles" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <SkipLink client:load />
    <Header client:load />
    <Hero client:load />
    <main id="main-content" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row max-w-7xl mx-auto p-4">
      <section class="flex-1 p-4 space-y-8">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Demo Page with Placeholder Content</h1>
        <article class="prose max-w-none">
          <h2>Sample Article Title</h2>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed euismod, nisl vel tincidunt fermentum, nunc sapien bibendum nulla, nec egestas justo sapien at justo.</p>
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x400" alt="Placeholder" />
          <p>Aliquam erat volutpat. Integer sit amet convallis urna. Nulla facilisi. Curabitur at elit sit amet elit sollicitudin cursus.</p>
          <h3>Subheading</h3>
          <p>Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia curae; Integer nec odio. Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam.</p>
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x300" alt="Placeholder" />
          <p>Suspendisse potenti. Morbi mattis ullamcorper velit. Phasellus gravida semper nisi. Nullam vel sem.</p>
        </article>
      </section>
      <Sidebar client:load />
    </main>
    <NewsletterModal client:load />
  </body>
</html>